\centerline{Meguro-ku, Tokyo 153 JAPAN}
%if too many authors for abstract on same page, say   \vfill\eject\pageno0

\vskip .3in
Abstract. We propose a new $q$-series formula for a character of
parafermion conformal field theories associated to
arbitrary non-twisted affine Lie algebra $\widehat{g}$.
%
We show its natural origin from a thermodynamic Bethe
ansatz analysis including chemical potentials.


\Date{12/92}

